(120,1,'2014-06-29 20:24:58','2014-06-29 20:24:58','<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">Some entrepreneurs fight to get their foot in the door.</h1>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\">We open doors for our ventures and alumni.</h1>\n<h2 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #008ff0;\" href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/programs/\">APPLY TO A SEED SPOT PROGRAM</a></h2>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Making new connections can take a lot of time. Bouncing around conferences, networking events and even cold calling leaves a lot to chance. Over the past threeyears, SEED SPOT has curated the best people we can find - from Emmy-winning graphic designers to CEOs who have cashed out big, and everything between. One of the core benefits of being aSEED SPOT venture is plugging into this network.</p>\n[pexservices pex_attr_set=\"network-graphic-1\" pex_attr_layout=\"icon\" pex_attr_columns=\"4\" pex_attr_parallax=\"disabled\" pex_attr_crop=\"enabled\" pex_attr_undefined=\"undefined\" pex_attr_title=\"\" pex_attr_desc=\"\" pex_attr_btntext=\"\" pex_attr_btnlink=\"\"][/pexservices]\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"&quot;NO ANSWERS ARE FOUND WITHIN THIS BUILDING&quot;\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">At SEED SPOT, we know that nothing happens without a network of people supporting you. We push every single venture to spend the majority of their time out connecting with clients, customers and partners. No amount of classroom education can substitute forthe value of real feedback from the market. What we see in our performance tracking data is that great entrepreneurs develop through interactions in the community.</p>\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"EXTRAORDINARY LEVELS OF SUPPORT\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">The SEED SPOT Network often provides ventures free or reduced-cost services to thosethat spark their interest and passion. Accountants donate services; so do attorneys, designers, industry-specific consultants and a myriad of other professionals in Phoenix and around the globe. Among the many benefits of being incubated and / or accelerated at SEED SPOT is finding these people on Day 2 of your journey, instead of Day 200.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #298df2;\" href=\"mailto:corinn@seedspot.org?subject=I\'d like to join the SS Network!\">JOIN THE NETWORK</a></p>','SEED SPOT NETWORK','','publish','closed','closed','','seedspot-network','','','2014-06-29 20:24:58','2014-06-29 20:24:58','',0,'http://seedspot.wpengine.com/?page_id=120',0,'page','',0),
