(127,1,'2014-07-02 13:52:15','2014-07-02 13:52:15','[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"GREAT LEADERS HAVE GREAT MENTORS\" pex_attr_button_text=\"BECOME A SEED SPOT MENTOR\" pex_attr_button_link=\"http://www.jotform.us/Seedspot/mentor-apply\" pex_attr_button_color=\"008ff0\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\nWe believe that problems aren\'t solved in isolation; problems are solved by finding people with the expertise, energyand connections to build solutions. The most importantthing we do for our ventures is help them build a circle of trusted mentors who coach, audit and accelerate their work. Each venture is matched with mentors who\'s experience they can leverage throughout their SEED SPOT journey, and beyond.\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"\" pex_attr_title=\"RELATIONSHIPS BUILT TO LAST\" pex_attr_button_text=\"\" pex_attr_button_link=\"\" pex_attr_button_color=\"\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\">We\'ve found that72% of mentor relationships have lasted beyond their official program trackat SEED SPOT. While our programs are based on professional support and guidance, we see personal friendships blossom. Weve also seen mentors invest and join advisory boards of many ventures, which is a big winfor everyone.</p>\n<p class=\"p2\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #008ff0;\">MEET OUR CURRENT MENTORS</a></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n[pexcarousel pex_attr_cat=\"172\" pex_attr_spacing=\"true\" pex_attr_orderby=\"date\" pex_attr_order=\"DESC\"][/pexcarousel]','MENTORSHIP','','publish','closed','closed','','mentorship','','','2014-07-02 13:52:15','2014-07-02 13:52:15','',0,'http://seedspot.wpengine.com/?page_id=127',0,'page','',0),
