(140,1,'2014-07-02 14:09:48','2014-07-02 14:09:48','<h1 class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Our space reflects our culture: creative, comfortable &amp;playful.</h1>\n[pexcarousel pex_attr_cat=\"60\" pex_attr_title=\"\" pex_attr_link=\"\" pex_attr_link_title=\"\" pex_attr_maxnum=\"\" pex_attr_spacing=\"true\" pex_attr_orderby=\"menu_order\" pex_attr_order=\"DESC\"][/pexcarousel]\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n<div class=\"cols-wrapper cols-3\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<div class=\"col\">\n<ul class=\"bullet_arrow4 imglist\">\n	<li>Our building is in the heart of Central Phoenix with a light rail stop right at the corner of our intersection. We\'ve got 3balconies with stunning views of the city.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\">\n<ul class=\"bullet_arrow4 imglist\">\n	<li style=\"text-align: left;\">In total, we have 27private offices, 15private desks, 5 shared desks, 3 conference rooms, 2 balconies and 1 classroom in addition to open venue space on both sides of the floor.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"col nomargin\">\n<ul class=\"bullet_arrow4 imglist\">\n	<li>When you arrive at SEED SPOT, youll be greeted by our very own patron saint, Oscar, who both runsthe parking garage and serves as de facto loving neighbor to every venture.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Whatever event you\'re planning, we\'ve got the space to accommodate you.We\'ve hosted everything from Board Meetings to a High School Prom!</span></strong>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">+ Club, Staff, Corporate Retreats</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">+ Casual to Semi-Formal Event Venue Space</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">+ Offsite Meetings</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">+ Private Office Rentals</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">+ Open Desk Space Rentals</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">+ Team Building Sessions</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">+ Nonprofit, Corporate Partner &amp; Student Group Discounts Available</p>\n[pexpricetable pex_attr_set=\"seed-spot-office-space\" pex_attr_columns=\"4\" pex_attr_color=\"008ff0\"][/pexpricetable]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We give tours every Wednesday at 1pm!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Get directions --&gt; <a class=\"button\" href=\"mailto:corinn@seedspot.org\">I\'m coming to see SEED SPOT!</a></p>\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;','OUR OFFICE SPACE','','publish','closed','closed','','our-office-space','','','2014-07-02 14:09:48','2014-07-02 14:09:48','',0,'http://seedspot.wpengine.com/?page_id=140',0,'page','',0),
(141,1,'2014-07-02 14:09:19','2014-07-02 14:09:19','[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"\" pex_attr_title=\"PROPRIETARY CURRICULUM\" pex_attr_button_text=\"CHECK OUT OUR PROGRAMS\" pex_attr_button_link=\"http://www.seedspot.org/programs/\" pex_attr_button_color=\"008ff0\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<p class=\"p3\" style=\"text-align: center;\">There is nothing out there like the SEED SPOT Curriculum.</p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">SEED SPOT surrounds each entrepreneur with all the resources she/he needs to thrive. Based on lean principles, the SEED SPOT curriculum has been developed to combine the best practices of startup development and social enterprise development. Each program uses the SEED SPOT Canvas, a tool focused on business model development with impact at the core, to guide entrepreneurs through various programs.</span></p>\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"\" pex_attr_title=\"CONTENT EXPERTS\" pex_attr_button_text=\"VOLUNTEER YOUR EXPERTISE\" pex_attr_button_link=\"mailto:cpher@seedspot.org?subject=I&#39;d like to be a SEED SPOT Content Expert\" pex_attr_button_color=\"008ff0\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<p class=\"p3\" style=\"text-align: center;\">All of the sections of our Full-Time curriculumfeature at least one expert guest who has actually gone out and done what theyre talking about. So when you learn about raising capital, its from someone who has actually raised it. When you learn about advertising on social media, its from someone who has sold products using that channel. This is true for every step of the program.</p>\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"1 on 1 COACHING\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<p class=\"p3\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Each week, we sit down with each venture and tailor their educational experience. Some people need to start at square one; others need support in a few key areas.We put together a plan thats tailored to meet the needs off each venture.</p>\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"LEADERSHIP DEVELOPMENT\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">The entrepreneur themselves is just important as the business. We are sure to take a step back from working \"in\" the venture, and help the entrepreneurs to look within in order to improve their success of working \"on\" the business.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #008ff0;\" href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/seed-spot-2015-apply-step-1/\">APPLY TO SEED SPOT</a></p>','CURRICULUM','','publish','closed','closed','','education-training','','','2014-07-02 14:09:19','2014-07-02 14:09:19','',0,'http://seedspot.wpengine.com/?page_id=141',0,'page','',0),
