(817,1,'2015-05-14 21:48:43','2015-05-15 04:48:43','<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #b8430e;\" href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/seed-spot-2015-apply-step-1/\">APPLY NOW</a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Multiple times a year, SEED SPOT runs 5-Day Boot Camps to help entrepreneurs launch their dreams. Entrepreneurs are guided through a business model generation curriculum, surrounded by experts, and mentored by community leaders for 5-Days. To provide a safe and supportive environment for entrepreneurs, several of the Bootcamps are designed for specific demographics.</div>\n<div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"highlight1\">SEED SPOT Boot Camps are perfect for entrepreneurs who have an idea and want to bring it to life.</span></div>\n<a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/unnamed-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"216\" height=\"172\" /></a>\n\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DESIGNED FOR RAPID LEARNING</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">30 HOURS OF TRAINING</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">BUILDING BUSINESS MODELS</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CUSTOMERVALIDATION</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">LEGAL 101</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MARKETING 101</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">HOW TO BUILD NETWORKS</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DEVELOPING A PITCH</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">NETWORKING LUNCHEONS</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MENTORSHIP FROM ROCKSTARS</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ACCESS TO INVESTORS</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ACCESS TO $10,000, 0% LOAN</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">FEE $750</p>\n&nbsp;\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>UPCOMING BOOT CAMP DATES</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">WOMEN\'S BOOT CAMP JANUARY 25-29 2016</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">FEBRUARY 29-MARCH 4 2016</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MARCH 14-18 2016</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MARCH 28-APRIL 1 2016</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MAY 16-20 2016</p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #b8430e;\" href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/seed-spot-2015-apply-step-1/\">APPLY NOW</a></div>','5 DAY BOOT CAMPS','','publish','closed','closed','','5-day-bootcamps','','','2015-05-14 21:48:43','2015-05-15 04:48:43','',0,'http://www.seedspot.org/?page_id=817',0,'page','',0),
(818,1,'2015-05-14 21:48:52','2015-05-15 04:48:52','<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n<a class=\"button\" href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/seed-spot-2015-apply-step-1/\">APPLY</a>\n\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n<hr />\n\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Twice annually, SEED SPOT\'s 12-week Evening Program works with entrepreneurs that have great ideas and want to bring them to life. Entrepreneurs are surrounded by the support they need to launch their dreams. During the Evening Program, entrepreneurs have access to a top tier curriculum, SEED SPOT experts, and speed mentoring sessions. Meeting every <span class=\"aBn\" tabindex=\"0\" data-term=\"goog_240428195\"><span class=\"aQJ\">Monday</span></span> for 12-weeks, the Evening Program creates a community of entrepreneurs supporting each other.</div>\n<div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">The SEED SPOT Evening Program is a great fit for entrepreneurs that have just started their journey in starting company or are thinking about starting a company.</div>\n<a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/unnamed.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"206\" height=\"195\" /></a>\n\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DESIGNED FOR LAUNCH STAGE</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">12 WEEKS OF TRAINING</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">1 NIGHT PER WEEK 5:30-7PM</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DEFINING BUSINESS MODEL</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">UNDERSTANDING CUSTOMERS</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">VALUE PROPOSITION</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">BRANDING</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">LEGAL</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">BUILD COST STRUCTURES</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">WORK ON REVENUE MODEL</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MENTOR NIGHT</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">PEER PITCH PRACTICE</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ACCESS TO $10,000, 0% LOAN</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">FEE: $1,000</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">SEPT 8-NOV 30 2015</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">FEB 22 - MAY 9 2016</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/seed-spot-2015-apply-step-1/\">APPLY</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>','EVENING PROGRAM','','publish','closed','closed','','evening-program','','','2015-05-14 21:48:52','2015-05-15 04:48:52','',0,'http://www.seedspot.org/?page_id=818',0,'page','',0),
(819,1,'2015-05-14 21:49:02','2015-05-15 04:49:02','<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p class=\"p1\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/seed-spot-2015-apply-step-1/\">APPLY</a></p>\n\n\n<hr />\n\n<div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">Every Fall, SEED SPOT works with a set of highly motivated social entrepreneurs for the 14-week Full-time Program. During the program, entrepreneurs are surrounded by experts, mentors, office space, and access to financing opportunities, to take their businesses to the next level. The Full-time Program culminates with each Full Time venture presenting at Demo Day, the largest entrepreneurial event in Arizona.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">The SEED SPOT Full-time program is perfect for the entrepreneur that has started their business and want to take it to the next level.</div>\n</div>\n<div>\n\n<a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/unnamed-3.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"233\" height=\"186\" /></a>\n\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DESIGNED FOR GROWTH STAGE</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">14 WEEKS OF TRAINING</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">30 HOURS PER WEEK</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">OFFICE SPACE PROVIDED</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DEEP DIVE ON BUSINESS MODEL</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">BRANDING, LEGAL, OPERATIONS</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">IN DEPTH WEEKLY COACHING</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">1:1 MENTORING</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">LEADERSHIP DEVELOPMENT</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">FINANCING OPPORTUNITITES</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">CAPITAL RAISING</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">MEDIA EXPOSURE</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ACCESS TO $10,000, 0% LOAN</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">WEEKLY PITCH PRACTICE</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ACCREDITED INVESTOR EVENT</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">DEMO DAY - BIG AUDIENCE!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">FEE: $3,500</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">SEPT 8-DEC 10 2015</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/seed-spot-2015-apply-step-1/\">APPLY</a></p>\n\n</div>','FULL-TIME PROGRAM','','publish','closed','closed','','full-time-program','','','2015-05-14 21:49:02','2015-05-15 04:49:02','',0,'http://www.seedspot.org/?page_id=819',0,'page','',0),
(824,1,'2015-05-14 21:52:26','2015-05-15 04:52:26','<h2 class=\"page-heading\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>VNDEME TU SUEO - FOLLOW THE JOURNEY!</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/SY6cDqTCc44\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n\n<h2 class=\"page-heading\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Made possible with support from</h2>\n<div class=\"cols-wrapper cols-2\">\n<div class=\"col\">\n\n<img class=\"img-frame  aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/08/logo_QuarlesBrady.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"196\" height=\"110\" />\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col nomargin\">\n\n<img class=\"img-frame  aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/blackstone_charitable_foudation_seed_spot.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"196\" height=\"101\" />\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Congratulations to the Top3 Finalists who will join SEED SPOT\'s Full-Time Program in the Fall!</strong></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div class=\"cols-wrapper cols-3\">\n<div class=\"col\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Adriana Grado &amp; </strong><strong>Yasmin Tapia</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame  alignnone\" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Adriana_Gradoheadshot.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"110\" height=\"183\" /></a><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame \" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Tapia_Yasmin-Headshot-.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"125\" height=\"183\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> Maingo</strong></p>\nA mobile app designed to increase the number of college students that order from and support local restaurants by making it simple for them to order delivery to their dorm room or apartment. Maingo aspires to build a network of college \"delivery\" drivers that like Uber can turn on/off their ability to pickup and deliver food to their peers while earning extra money and supporting the local economy.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Aditi Madane</strong></p>\n\n<div><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame  aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/IMG_4682.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"152\" height=\"169\" /></a></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>COMMUN.ITY</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">With a mission to build friendlier neighborhoods, Commun.ity is building an online marketplace where individuals can request help for the big and small things in life from other people who live in their neighborhood? Need your lawn mowed? Running late from a meeting and need someone to pickup your dog from the groomer? Commun.ity is the platform to post your needs and for your neighborhood to respond with help.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col nomargin\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Israel Medellin</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame  aligncenter\" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/Israel-Medellin.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"152\" height=\"171\" /></a> </strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Lucysgarage.com</strong></p>\nConnecting car-owners with local, experienced, or off-duty mechanics in a safe, secure, online platform with the intention of increasing connection between talented mechanics and those who need them. The goal is to keep the money local and build a trusted network of mechanic professionals and provide a steady stream of business opportunities to them.\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n<hr />\n\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">TOP 20 SEMIFINALISTS</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame \" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/05/foto-ganadores.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n<hr />\n\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n[pexcarousel pex_attr_cat=\"56\" pex_attr_title=\"Meet the Top 20 Semifinalists!\" pex_attr_link=\"\" pex_attr_link_title=\"Vndeme tu Sueo Top 20\" pex_attr_maxnum=\"20\" pex_attr_spacing=\"false\" pex_attr_orderby=\"date\" pex_attr_order=\"ASC\"][/pexcarousel]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Casting Call - Sneak Peek May 16th, 2015</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://univisionarizona.univision.com/vendeme-tus-suenos/video/2015-05-16/sneak-peek-vendeme-de-tu-sueno/embed\" width=\"592\" height=\"333\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Episode One - DEMO DAY Preview!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://univisionarizona.univision.com/vendeme-tus-suenos/episodios/video/2015-05-21/la-locura-de-las-audiciones-episodio-1/embed\" width=\"592\" height=\"333\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Semifinalists Presented at DEMO DAY</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://univisionarizona.univision.com/vendeme-tus-suenos/videos/video/2015-05-20/presentan-semifinalistas-de-vendeme-tu-sueno/embed\" width=\"592\" height=\"333\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Episode 2 - Meet Elsa Leon</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://univisionarizona.univision.com/vendeme-tus-suenos/episodios/video/2015-05-29/vendeme-tu-sueno-episodio-2/embed\" width=\"592\" height=\"333\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Episode 3 - Meet Christopher Angulo</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"http://univisionarizona.univision.com/vendeme-tus-suenos/episodios/video/2015-06-04/joven-e-innovador-empresario-episodio-3/embed\" width=\"592\" height=\"333\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>','VNDEME TU SUEO','','publish','closed','closed','','vendeme-tu-sueno','','','2015-05-14 21:52:26','2015-05-15 04:52:26','',0,'http://www.seedspot.org/?page_id=824',0,'page','',0),
