(1077,1,'2014-05-22 09:49:46','2014-05-22 16:49:46','<a href=\"http://www.bizjournals.com/phoenix/blog/techflash/2014/05/seed-spot-warms-up-for-third-demo-day.html\">Read the full article here.</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n<div><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame \" src=\"http://www.seedspot.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/06/Screen-shot-2015-06-24-at-2.35.41-PM-1.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n\n<!--more-->\n\n<hr />\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"detail__meta\"><time></time><strong>What:</strong> Seed Spots third Demo Day has 12 Arizona-based entrepreneurs given three minutes to share their socially responsible, purpose-driven business plan.</div>\n<div class=\"detail__meta\">\n<p class=\"content__segment\"><strong>When:</strong> 5:30-7:30 p.m. june 5 Where: Orpheum Theatre, 203 W. Adams St., Phoenix</p>\n\n<aside class=\"inset inset--major hidden--print\">\n<div class=\"ad-container ad-container--in-inset\"></div>\n</aside>\n<p class=\"content__segment\"><strong>Why:</strong> Seed Spot is a Phoenix-based nonprofit incubator that works with social entrepreneurs committed to solving important societal problems. It provides resources, curriculum, mentors, financial modeling, pitch development and capital opportunities for chosen entrepreneurs.</p>\n<p class=\"content__segment\">Demo Day is the culmination of the four-month, full-time Seed Spot program. Audience members will get to vote via text message for their favorite venture, which will then receive a $5,000 cash prize. Other awards will also be given out.</p>\n<p class=\"content__segment\"><strong>Facts:</strong> Seed Spot has provided 15,640 hours of mentorship, graduated 34 entrepreneurs, helped secure more than $1 million in capital, created 61 jobs and positively impacted the lives of more than 56,000 people.</p>\n<p class=\"content__segment\"><strong>Cost:</strong> <a href=\"http://ssdemoday.splashthat.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Free RSVP</a>.</p>\n\n<div class=\"content__segment\"></div>\n</div>','Phoenix Business Journal: SEED SPOT warms up for third DEMO DAY','','publish','closed','closed','','phoenix-business-journal-seed-spot-warms-up-for-third-demo-day','','','2014-05-22 09:49:46','2014-05-22 16:49:46','',0,'http://www.seedspot.org/?p=1077',0,'post','',0),
