(1212,1,'2015-07-13 12:55:26','2015-07-13 19:55:26','[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"OUR MISSION\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>TO EDUCATE, ACCELERATE, AND INVEST IN ENTREPRENEURS </b></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>WHO ARE CREATING SOLUTIONS TO SOCIAL PROBLEMS.</b></p>\n\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[pexservices pex_attr_set=\"default\" pex_attr_layout=\"icon\" pex_attr_columns=\"4\" pex_attr_parallax=\"disabled\" pex_attr_crop=\"enabled\" pex_attr_undefined=\"undefined\" pex_attr_title=\"\" pex_attr_desc=\"\" pex_attr_btntext=\"\" pex_attr_btnlink=\"\"][/pexservices]\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"CORE VALUES\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<div class=\"cols-wrapper cols-3\">\n<div class=\"col\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong>WELCOME ALL DREAMERS</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We embrace diversity and take entrepreneurs others turn away. We work with entrepreneurs of all ages, genders, ethnicities, socio-economic backgrounds and physical/developmental abilities. #DiverseEntrepreneurship #InclusiveInnovation</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n<span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong>BUILD COMMUNITY</strong></span>\n\nWe believe in building communities around entrepreneurs. We leverage existing resources, host a crazy amount of events, and see ourselves as a place where many people can plug in to support social entrepreneurs.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col nomargin\">\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong><span class=\"s1\">PROTECT THE ENTREPRENEUR</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"s1\">We believe in protecting the entrepreneur, we do not take equity in ventures, and we fight hard to keep folks away that are looking to take advantage of entrepreneurs. NO sharking or exploitation allowed.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cols-wrapper cols-2\">\n<div class=\"col\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong>RAISE THE BAR</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We believe in pushing the envelope. We take risks. We are wiling to fail, willing to take the jump, and encourage entrepreneurs to do the same.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col nomargin\">\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong><span class=\"s1\">BELIEVE ANYTHING IS POSSIBLE</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"s1\">We believe that optimism and a positive problem solving attitude is a powerful tool for making shit happen. We push ourselves and entrepreneurs to make the impossible, possible.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"\" pex_attr_title=\"OUR METHOD\" pex_attr_button_text=\"\" pex_attr_button_link=\"\" pex_attr_button_color=\"\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<div><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" href=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/pasted_image_at_2015_08_06_01_09_pm_720.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/pasted_image_at_2015_08_06_01_09_pm_720.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">We do not take equity in our ventures - we surround themwith the support they need to succeed and impact the world.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">We offer a <a href=\"http://bit.ly/seedspotprograms\">diverse selection of programs </a>to benefit allentrepreneurs.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n</div>\n<div></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"OUR IMPACT\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\n[pexservices pex_attr_set=\"metrics\" pex_attr_layout=\"icon\" pex_attr_columns=\"3\" pex_attr_parallax=\"disabled\" pex_attr_crop=\"enabled\" pex_attr_undefined=\"undefined\" pex_attr_title=\"\" pex_attr_desc=\"\" pex_attr_btntext=\"\" pex_attr_btnlink=\"\"][/pexservices]\n<div><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" href=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Commitment-to-Transparency-Recognized-by-Intelligent-Philanthropy.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/Commitment-to-Transparency-Recognized-by-Intelligent-Philanthropy.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"262\" height=\"141\" /></a></div>\n<div>\n\n<hr />\n\n</div>\n<div>\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"SEED SPOT\" pex_attr_title=\"FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS\" pex_attr_button_text=\"\" pex_attr_button_link=\"\" pex_attr_button_color=\"\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\nWhat is SEED SPOT?\n\nSEED SPOT is a nonprofit organization with a mission to educate, accelerate, and invest in entrepreneurs who are creating solutions to social problems.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWhen and where was SEED SPOT founded?\n\nSEED SPOT was founded in Phoenix, AZ in 2012.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWhat is SEED SPOTs mission?\n\nTo educate, accelerate, and invest in entrepreneurs who are creating solutions to social problems.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWhere did the name come from?\n\nAt SEED SPOT, we fundamentally believe that everyone has a seed of an idea inside of them, but very few have the courage to pursue it. SEED SPOT was named for that reason, as the spot where courage could be found and seeds of ideas could grow into organizations and companies that change the world.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nIs SEED SPOT a nonprofit or a for-profit?\n\nSEED SPOT is a 501(c)3 nonprofit. We believe that by being a nonprofit we are able to be a community resource for all social entrepreneurs.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWhat is SEED SPOTs EIN number?\n\n45-4098436\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWhat Social Entrepreneurship?\n\n<strong>Social entrepreneurs create systemic solutions to social issues through the use of business principles</strong>. A social entrepreneur can found a company or organization that is for-profit or non-profit. When it comes to solving problems there are no boundaries.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWhat is SEED SPOT NEXT?\n\nSEED SPOT NEXT is a high school program designed to partner with schools that are serious about educating their students about how to become change agents and social entrepreneurs. We leverage a model by which we train teachers on high school campuses and equip them with the curriculum, tools, materials, and connections to help bring student passions to life. To learn more about SEED SPOT NEXT, please visitthe <a href=\"http://www.seedspotnext.org\">High School Program page</a>.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"\" pex_attr_title=\"PROGRAMS AND SUPPORT FREQUENTLY ASKED QUESTIONS\" pex_attr_button_text=\"\" pex_attr_button_link=\"\" pex_attr_button_color=\"\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\nWhat are SEED SPOTs programs?\n\nSEED SPOT offers several programs aimed at different stages of a startups growth. We have 2 Day workshops, 5 Day Boot Camps, 12 Week Evening Program, and a 14 Week Full Time Program.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nDoes SEED SPOT take equity?\n\nNope. SEED SPOT does not receive equity in exchange for ventures participating in SEED SPOT programs.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nDo the ventures pay to be a part of your programs?\n\nYes, the program fees range from $500 - $3,500. Our programs are heavily subsidized through philanthropic support and the value an entrepreneur receives from our program is many multiples of the program fee.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nCan a team go through SEED SPOT programs?\n\nYes! Each program is designed for either teams or individual entrepreneurs to attend. A team is responsible for one program fee.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nCan nonprofits attend SEED SPOTs programs?\n\nYes! We love helping new nonprofits start and grow their impact.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nIs SEED SPOT a co-working space?\n\nNot really, but we have lots of options to use our space. SEED SPOT has a collaborative working space that is available to SEED SPOT ventures during programs and as alumni.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWe have flexible working space available for short or long-term leases. We also open up our space for events and offsite meetings. To learn more, please visit our <a href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/our-office-space/\">office space page</a>:\n\n&nbsp;\n\nI am interested in seeing SEED SPOT, when can I have a tour?\n\nWe offer tours once a week on Wednesdays at 1pm.\n\nWe also have open houses that go over our programs and give you tours of our space. Check out the <a href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/calendar/\">events page</a> to attend our next open house\n\n&nbsp;\n\nI am interested in learning more about SEED SPOT programs, how can I learn more?\n\nWe have open houses that go over our programs and give you tours of our space. Another great option is to attend a Venture Friday to hear ventures pitch and talk with current ventures. Check out the <a href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/calendar/\">events page</a> to see the next open house or Venture Friday.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nWhat is Venture Friday?\n\nEvery Friday during Full Time programming, SEED SPOT Ventures pitch their business for 3 minutes to a community audience. The community provides advice, feedback, and connections to help the ventures pursue their dream. After pitches, there is pizza and networking! Check our <a href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/calendar/\">calendar</a> to see when there is a Venture Friday happening.\n\n&nbsp;\n\nDoes SEED SPOT partner with organizations?\n\nYou bet we do! We love partnering with other organizations to help entrepreneurs pursue their dreams. A great example of an organization we have partnered with is, Univision Arizona. Through our partnership, we launched Vndeme tu Sueo, a program to help Latino entrepreneurs launch their businesses.\n\n</div>\n&nbsp;\n\nCan SEED SPOTsupport entrepreneurs in my city?\n\nAlthough we have entrepreneurs who come to Phoenix for our programs, we have not yet launched outside of Arizona YET. If you think your city would be a great fit for SEED SPOT, <a href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/bring-seed-spot-to-your-city/\">let us know!</a>','ABOUT US','','publish','closed','closed','','about-us','','','2015-07-13 12:55:26','2015-07-13 19:55:26','',0,'http://www.seedspot.org/?page_id=1212',0,'page','',0),
