(1347,1,'2015-07-14 10:14:35','2015-07-14 17:14:35','<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"button\" style=\"background-color: #b8430e;\" href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/become-a-recruitment-partner/\">APPLY TO HAVE YOUR LOGO ON OUR RECRUITMENTPARTNER PAGE</a></p>\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"RECRUITMENT PARTNER\" pex_attr_title=\"FACEBOOK POST\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\nDo you want to change the world? If yes, apply to SEED SPOT to launch your dream business! Apply today: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/seedspotprograms\">bit.ly/seedspotprograms</a> #socent #SEEDSPOT\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Dream of being your own boss and making the world a better place? SEED SPOT can help you launch! Learn more here: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/seedspotprograms\">bit.ly/seedspotprograms</a> </span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">SEED SPOT, Arizona\'s Social Impact Incubator, is recruiting the next class of entrepreneurs that are looking to change the world. SEED SPOT offers programs to help entreprenuers from an inkling of idea to growing nationally and internationally. Learn more here: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/seedspotprograms\">bit.ly/seedspotprograms</a></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Need help starting your business? SEED SPOT, a non-profit, is here to help you grow your business and make impact in the world. Learn more here: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/seedspotprograms\">bit.ly/seedspotprograms</a></span></p>\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"RECRUITMENT PARTNER\" pex_attr_title=\"TWEETS\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\n<a href=\"http://ctt.ec/eQf5s\" target=\"_blank\">CLICK TO TWEET</a>:Dream of starting your own business? Do it! Apply to @SEEDSPOTbit.ly/seedspotprograms#socent #seedspot\n\n<a href=\"http://ctt.ec/UhR2O\" target=\"_blank\">CLICK TO TWEET: </a>Ever want to be your own boss? Now is the time. Apply to @SEEDSPOTbit.ly/seedspotprograms#socent #seedspot\n\n<a href=\"http://ctt.ec/Jly20\" target=\"_blank\">CLICK TO TWEET:</a> Want help growing your business, but dont want to give up equity? Apply to @SEEDSPOTbit.ly/seedspotprograms#seedspot\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"RECRUITMENT PARTNER\" pex_attr_title=\"DIRECT INTRODUCTION TEMPLATE\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\nHi [name of entrepreneur],\n\nI wanted to introduce you to SEED SPOT, an early stage social entrepreneur incubator. They run several programs [link to programs page] to help you launch and grow your business! The programs range from 5-day Boot Camps to a 14-Week Full Time Program. SEED SPOT, a non-profit, is here to help you pursue your dream!\n\nI have cced Cpher, Director of Entrepreneur Initiatives at SEED SPOT, to answer any questions you might have!\n\nSincerely,\n\n[your name]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"RECRUITMENT FLIER\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<div>\n<div><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" href=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NoDeadline.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame  aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/NoDeadline.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n</div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"RECRUITMENT PARTNER\" pex_attr_title=\"DIRECT NEWSLETTER TEMPLATE\" pex_attr_button_text=\"\" pex_attr_button_link=\"\" pex_attr_button_color=\"\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\nDo you want to change the world by starting a business? SEED SPOT, a social entrepreneurship incubator, runs entrepreneurship programs to help you launch and grow your dream. SEED SPOT surrounds you with access to experts, mentors, investors, 0% interest loans, and a proven business curriculum to grow your business. SEED SPOT does not take equity in your company!\n\n1)  Full Time Program\n\n14-Weeks to grow your business\n\nWhen: September 8<sup>th</sup>  December 10<sup>th</sup>\n\nTime: 30 hours a week\n\nApply Today: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/seedspotfulltime\">bit.ly/seedspotfulltime</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n2)  Evening Program\n\n12-Weeks to launch your business\n\nWhen: September 8<sup>th</sup>  November 30<sup>th</sup>\n\nTime: 5:30pm-7pm, 1 night a week\n\nApply Today: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/seedspotevening\">bit.ly/seedspotevening</a>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n3) General SEED SPOT Boot Camp\n\n5-Days of rapid learning to make your idea a reality\n\nWhen: July 27-31, 9am-4:30pm\n\nApply Today:<a href=\"http://bit.ly/seedspotbootcamp\">bit.ly/seedspotbootcamp</a>\n\n</div>\n&nbsp;\n<div>\n\nIf you want to learn more about SEED SPOT Programs, come to an open house! bit.ly/seedspotopenhouse\n\n</div>\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"THANK YOU FOR YOUR HELP!\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\nTo acknowledge your help in making the entrepreneurial ecosystem more robust, we would love to list your organization, or affiliation on our recruitment partner page. If you would like to have your logo and name on the page, please fill out <a href=\"http://www.seedspot.org/become-a-recruitment-partner/\">THIS FORM.</a>','RECRUITMENT PARTNER TOOLS','','publish','closed','closed','','recruitment-partner-tools','','','2015-07-14 10:14:35','2015-07-14 17:14:35','',0,'http://www.seedspot.org/?page_id=1347',0,'page','',0),
