(1405,1,'2015-08-06 14:26:52','2015-08-06 21:26:52','&nbsp;\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"WHAT WE DO\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\">We educate, accelerate and invest in entrepreneurs creating solutions to social problems.</span></h2>\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_title=\"CORE VALUES\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<div class=\"cols-wrapper cols-3\">\n<div class=\"col\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong>WELCOME ALL DREAMERS</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We embrace diversity and take entrepreneurs others turn away. We work with entrepreneurs of all ages, genders, ethnicities, socio-economic backgrounds and physical/developmental abilities. #DiverseEntrepreneurship #InclusiveInnovation</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\n<span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong>BUILD COMMUNITY</strong></span>\n\nWe believe in building communities around entrepreneurs. We leverage existing resources, host a crazy amount of events, and see ourselves as a place where many people can plug in to support social entrepreneurs.\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col nomargin\">\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong><span class=\"s1\">PROTECT THE ENTREPRENEUR</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"s1\">We believe in protecting the entrepreneur, we do not take equity in ventures, and we fight hard to keep folks away that are looking to take advantage of entrepreneurs. NO sharking or exploitation allowed.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cols-wrapper cols-2\">\n<div class=\"col\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong>RAISE THE BAR</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We believe in pushing the envelope. We take risks. We are wiling to fail, willing to take the jump, and encourage entrepreneurs to do the same.</p>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"col nomargin\">\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong><span class=\"s1\">BELIEVE ANYTHING IS POSSIBLE</span></strong></span></p>\n<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"s1\">We believe that optimism and a positive problem solving attitude is a powerful tool for making shit happen. We push ourselves and entrepreneurs to make the impossible, possible.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"\" pex_attr_title=\"OUR METHOD\" pex_attr_button_text=\"\" pex_attr_button_link=\"\" pex_attr_button_color=\"\"][/pexcirclecta]\n<div><a class=\"lightbox-image\" title=\"\" href=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/pasted_image_at_2015_08_06_01_09_pm_720.png\" data-rel=\"lightbox\"><img class=\"img-frame  aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/pasted_image_at_2015_08_06_01_09_pm_720.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">We do not take equity in our ventures - we surround themwith the support they need to succeed and impact the world.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">We offer a <a href=\"http://bit.ly/seedspotprograms\">diverse selection of programs </a>to benefit allentrepreneurs.</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<hr />\n\n</div>\n<div></div>\n&nbsp;\n\n[pexcirclecta pex_attr_small_title=\"NOW IT\'S YOUR TURN\" pex_attr_title=\"SHOW US YOUR CITY\"][/pexcirclecta]\n\n<strong><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\">BE AN AMBASSADOR.</span></strong>\n\nAre you someone who spreads the word, loves #SocEnt and thrives on being a community connector? Do you believe in the SEED SPOT mission and want to grow it in your community? A SEED SPOT Ambassador can be anyone from an investor to a corporate leader to a community cultivator to a grassroots organizer. Whoever you are, we want to learn about your city from you. The bottom line is supporting social entrepreneurship.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\">GET CREATIVE.</span></strong>\n\nProve to us that your city can create a place for social entrepreneurs to thrive.\n\nShowus through your method of choice: Videos, playdough molds, powerpoints, napkin doodles, essay, iambic pentameter, smoke signals, morse code, cat memes - whatever works!\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<strong><span style=\"color: #b8430e;\">IMPORTANT THINGS TO INCLUDE.</span></strong>\n\nWhat makes your city special?\n\nHow could SEED SPOTpositively impact your community?Why SEED SPOT?\n\nWhere are social entrepreneurs getting the support they need right now?\n\nWho else believes in social entrepreneurship in your city?\n\n<script src=\"http://form.jotformpro.com/jsform/52175171826961\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style=\"color: #b8430e;\"><strong>NOMINATE ANAMBASSADOR.</strong></span>\n\nYoulove the mission and believe that your city needs support for social entrepreneurs and you know the exact person to tell your city\'s story.<a href=\"mailto:cpher@seedspot.org?subject=SEED SPOT Ambassador Introduction\">Introduce us to that person.</a>','START SEED SPOT  PHOENIX   (INSERT YOUR CITY HERE)','','publish','closed','closed','','your-city','','','2015-08-06 14:26:52','2015-08-06 21:26:52','',0,'http://www.seedspot.org/?page_id=1405',0,'page','',0),
